Interface ScriptingScript

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Observable, Script, ScriptingBaseScript, ScriptingUnit, WeakReferencingObservable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ScriptingDialog
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultScriptingDialog, DefaultScriptingScript

    public interface ScriptingScript
extends ScriptingBaseScript, Script

    Interface that represents a single script without window dialog.
